Author: pomp-and-regrets
Text: I never really get alone time, so I don't have the chance to really do exercises at home, and my knees are shit so I can't run without wrecking myself. I try to take a walk daily but it only ends up burning about 350 calories for an hour. Plus I really like the routine of a gym. I feel like it'll offer some sense of stability for me.  Thank you for the suggestion though. I really do appreciate it ❤️

Author: fruitluvr22
Text: Do you think you can do some at home exercises in your room in the meantime so your wallet doesn’t have to take a hit?
